認識，所以冇去深究"},{"pid":"af0882be620816a5c357ba13c2432e60791bae9d","tid":514394,"uid":76413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"同埋真係有料既你要自已識分<br />\ndw真係昆錢多<br />\n但好多真係有料既都要membership<br />\n一係要你磅水，一係就老撚咁難申請<br />\n冇乜探究精神就唔好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d55431cfd13725facc3e792cca6176f9427f6c","tid":514394,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過好老實講<br />\n你係directory度搵到既通常都流流地<br />\n可能去forum/bbs度仲多痴線野睇</blockquote><br />\n知得愈多愈傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>其實好多都係地下藝術野喎...<br />\n老老實實除一堆cp同戇鳩網好多都係昆水<br />\n不過間唔中都有好野，以前見過一個好多paper/journal既database<br />\n同埋好多都用俄/德文，冇心機睇都冇必要上</blockquote><br />\n有咩正野</blockquote>睇下你對乜有興趣啦<br />\npaper/journal既database個個應該就我見過最有用<br />\n好似轉網址定死鳩左就冇留意了<br />\n入面有幾多本身要錢買先睇到既paper，乜柒都有咁<br />\n<br />\n體驗師就冇手冇腳既女人都有好多<br />\n不過我見個堆就純粹係Fetish咁，冇佢講既咁誇張<br />\n應該就只係搵班殘疾既扑野影相咁...<br />\n<br />\n最多既咪cp，不過好多都封左<br />\n都有死唔斷氣既，封左就係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.techspot.com/images2/news/bigimage/2013/2013-10-02-image-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.techspot.com%2Fimages2%2Fnews%2Fbigimage%2F2013%2F2013-10-02-image-6.jpg&h=8facc34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講cp呢樣野真係反映到外國好撚多pedo<br />\n同埋大陸都好多<br />\n<br />\n利申對電腦同解密個堆冇乜認識，所以冇去深究</blockquote><br />\n咩係cp<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c284bacb293ecc1c7946870e476defb6181bf0","tid":514394,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d55431cfd13725facc3e792cca6176f9427f6c","tid":514394,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過好老實講<br />\n你係direct